<title>Kim jaratty РӘЖ254</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
.Dm               A
  Kim jaratty, samǵap ushqan qustardy,
.   Asus                    Dm
 Samǵap ushqan qustardy, samǵap ushqan qustardy?
.D7              Gm
 Kim jaratty, samǵap ushqan qustardy?
.Dm/A Asus/Dm
 Bizdiń Qudaı!

[V2]
 Kim jaratty, samsaǵan juldyzdardy,
 Samsaǵan juldyzdardy,samsaǵan juldyzdardy?
 Kim jaratty, samsaǵan juldyzdardy?
 Bizdiń Qudaı!

[V3]
 Kim jaratty, tolqyǵan teńizderdi,
 Tolqyǵan teńizderdi,tolqyǵan teńizderdi?
 Kim jaratty, tolqyǵan teńizderdi?
 Bizdiń Qudaı!

[V4]
 Kim jaratty, samǵap ushqan qustardy,
 Samsaǵan juldyzdardy, tolqyǵan teńizderdi?
 Kim jaratty, senimen de, meni,
 Bizdiń Qudaı!
 Kim jaratty, senimen de, meni,
 Bizdiń Qudaı!</lyrics>
<key>Dm</key>
</song>